def is_clothes_item(x:item):
    # Checks whether an item is a piece of clothing
    symbol is_clothes_item = is_clothes(x) and (is_clothes_shirt(x) or is_clothes_pants(x) or is_clo
thes_socks(x) or is_clothes_skirt(x))
    return is_clothes_item

def has_unvisited_clothes(basket:item):
    # Checks if there are unobserved clothes inside the basket
    symbol has_unvisited = exists o: item : is_clothes_item(o) and inside(o, basket) and not visited
(o)
    return has_unvisited

        if has_unvisited_clothes(basket):

                if is_clothes_item(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):

        determine_fabric_type(clothing)

        bind basket_for_clothes_2006: item where:

        foreach clothing: item:

                sort_clothes_by_type_and_fabric(clothing)

def is_fabric_determined(clothes:item):

    return visited(clothes)
